  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The VEPRO trial is a cross-over randomised controlled trial comparing 2 corrective lenses for
      patients with presbyopia. The aim of the study is to compare the effectiveness of two
      corrective lenses: an old generation (Varilux Comfort Orma Crizal) and a new generation
      (Varilux Panamic Orma Crizal) of corrective lenses prescribed in presbyopia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
